<TEXT>
<P>
The ministry said in a statement that at least 25 rebels of
separatist Liberation Tigers of Tamil Eelam (LTTE) were killed on
Sunday in an operation at Muhamalai in the northernmost Jaffna
peninsula, adding that three armored tanks were damaged in the
fighting.
</P>
