its is tentatively planned for April 26. "The main issue on the
agenda is where we are in the peace process," Abdel Rahman said.
</P>
<P>
Israeli and Palestinian negotiators will return to Washington on
Thursday for another 10-day round of negotiations over a final-
status framework agreement and the third phase further
redeployment. 
