<HEADLINE> WI Harper Group to Invest in E-Commerce in Asia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 3 (Xinhua) -- The US-based WI Harper Group today
said that it will raise funds of more than 500 million US dollars
to invest in e-commerce and Internet-related industries in Asian
areas.
</P>
<P>
Peter Liu, chairman of Group, said at a seminar which opened
here today that Asian areas are still lagging behind in Internet
development, and the largest opportunity and greatest market is in
China.
