established during the second half of this year with 300 million
US dollars.
</P>
<P>
The WI Harper Group last year raised 70 million US dollars for
a Beijing Hi-tech Development Fund in conjunction with Beijing
Enterprises Holding Limited, which has invested in more than 20
projects.
</P>
<P>
The two-day seminar, called "eBeijing-2000", sponsored by the
WI Harper Group, the Beijing Enterprises Holding Limited, Qinghua
University Enterprise Group, and the State Information Center, has
attracted more than 500 participants from home and abroad.
