opportunities and challenges to the country's textile industry,
Deputy Director of the State Administration of Textile Industry (
SATI) Wang Tiankai said here Friday.
</P>
<P>
He said that as the largest producer and exporter of textiles
and garments in the world, China is of international
competitiveness in terms of labor costs, resources, and
manufacturing facilities.
